Description :
        High schooler Rico is determined to make her grandfather's karate dojo go viral, constantly posting on social media.
Just as she's searching for the next trending topic, an alien appears?!
A story of an unlikely friendship between an Earthling and a space visitor begins!
Source: MangaPlus
